text: Andi Prifti (born 1 August 1988 in Fier) is an Albanian footballer who most recently played for Apolonia Fier in the Albanian First Division.Soccerway profile His younger brother Albi also plays for Apolonia Fier. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Fier Category:Association football defenders Category:Albanian footballers Category:KF Apolonia Fier players Category:KS Albpetrol Patos players Category:KF Çlirimi players Category:KF Korabi Peshkopi players Category:KF Bylis Ballsh players Category:Albanian Superliga players Category:Albanian First Division players Category:Albanian Second Division players
